The Dark Exile <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umerlman.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Merlman</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/20/01 3:07:43 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Get your Book of Souls - solo</span><hr size=1> Another option for an instant gate potion is the Thurg gate potion. You make this as part of the Thurg shawl quest. anyone with a little pottery skill can make them and they cost nothing but a little time. This potion puts you on the bridge in thurg between the zone in and the front gate. This is much easier to get than the cap.<br>
