Not that that'll save the wizzie from a ghast HT. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvermintide.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vermintide</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/26/01 2:11:57 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Get your Book of Souls - solo</span><hr size=1> Last time I got the book myself, I had a wiz port me up.  A raid was there that had been in progress for a few hours, but the maestro room was fully popped.<br>
<br>
